title: Chile Hourly Wages in Manufacturing Index
description: Wages in Manufacturing in Chile decreased to 142.73 points in September from 143.38 points in August of 2022. Wages in Manufacturing in Chile averaged 117.09 points from 2009 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 143.51 points in December of 2015 and a record low of 97.75 points in February of 2016. This page provides - Chile Hourly Wages in Manufacturing Index - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Institute of Statistics, Chile
